84
00:03:28,080 --> 00:03:30,400
DAG. DAG stands for the directed as

85
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:33,280
cyclic graph. Each processing step is a

86
00:03:33,280 --> 00:03:35,680
note. Dependencies are edges. The

87
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:38,159
