88
00:03:38,159 --> 00:03:39,680
can complete without circular

89
00:03:39,680 --> 00:03:42,799
dependencies. First split the video into

90
00:03:42,799 --> 00:03:45,200
segments. Videos have key frames every

91
00:03:45,200 --> 00:03:47,599
