92
00:03:47,599 --> 00:03:50,080
alone without referencing others. Split

93
00:03:50,080 --> 00:03:52,720
a key frames now use segment processes

94
00:03:52,720 --> 00:03:55,360
independently. The workflow splits into

95
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:58,159
multiple streams. Video, audio, and

96
00:03:58,159 --> 00:04:00,319
